data.description: WELCOME HOME! This charming 3-bed, 2.5-bath home offers a serene and peaceful setting that's perfect for those dreaming of their own minifarm or seeking a tranquil lifestyle, nestled on 1.74 acres. The possibilities are endless! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open concept living room with a cozy stone finished fireplace. This seamless layout flows effortlessly into the dining area and kitchen, creating an inviting atmosphere that's perfect for entertaining. The primary first floor suite offers a completely remodeled bathroom w/heated marble floors, marble shower, large soaking tub and a BT speaker. Talk about a retreat! Enjoy hosting family and friends this holiday season with an upstairs flex room and the large bonus room that includes a wet bar and half bath. The entertaining does not stop there! Step outside onto the private back deck, a perfect spot to savor your morning coffee or enjoy a cool evening swim in the saltwater pool while watching a beautiful NC sunset.   Roof(22), HVAC(22/23), water filtration system, encapsulated CS, two workshops with electricity, & SS Refrigerator
